      "text": "Search Workflow\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\u2460 Identify protocol type\n\u2461 Load index.json protocolContext\n\u2462 Load relevant manifests (1-3)\n\u2463 Find patterns by keyword/severity\n\u2464 read_file(lineStart, lineEnd)\n\u2465 Apply patterns to target code\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n~200-500 lines read (vs 5000+)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "el_545798",
      "originalText": "Search Workflow\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n\u2460 Identify protocol type\n\u2461 Load index.json protocolContext\n\u2462 Load relevant manifests (1-3)\n\u2463 Find patterns by keyword/severity\n\u2464 read_file(lineStart, lineEnd)\n\u2465 Apply patterns to target code\n\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\u2501\n~200-500 lines read (vs 5000+)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
